race.comment: ROYALIFY (6) pushed forward and went on to record a determined win when resuming last start over 1200m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Can build off that and can make it two on the bounce. ROTHO BRO (5) settled well back but hit the line hard to win stylishly over this course and distance last start to maintain his good form of late. Sure to get back again from the draw but will be launching late. SAINT PHILOMENA (7) got well back over 1600m at Randwick last time and never threatened. Will appreciate a return to the country circuit and can make her presence felt. EILRAHC (9) was a barnstorming winner here last time and can keep the ball rolling on the quick back-up.
